msgstr ""
"<p>Most websites send emails when someone submits a contact form or when a new order arrives, but <strong>not every Hosting</strong> provider <strong>allows users to send</strong> mail via a <strong>PHP</strong> function or send <strong>SMTP mail using a domain name.</strong></p>\n"
"            <p>The <strong>SMTP mail</strong> feature allows users to <strong>configure email sending</strong> easily, quickly, and at no extra cost.</p>\n"
"            <a href=\"https://wiki.matbao.net/kb/thong-tin-smtp-gmail-cach-cau-hinh-smtp-gmail-free-vao-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\">View setup guide</a>"

